{"tid":828942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千人斬:加州情侶酒吧獵艷 迷暈性侵千女","createTime":"2018-09-20T04:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T09:32:49.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3affd2476ce064b36716b74dbe7220ff7c904d","tid":828942,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"美國加州一名曾在相親電視節目亮相的男醫生及其教師女友，上周二因迷姦兩名女子而被起訴。在調查過程之中，探員在該醫生的手機內，赫然發現大量意識不清裸女被侵犯的短片，發現兩人憑藉出眾外貌，數年內或哄騙了逾千名受害人。<br />\n憑出眾外表誘入住所迷姦<br />\n三十八歲骨科醫生羅比切奧斯外形俊朗，被指與其三十一歲教師女友賴利合謀，在海灘旁的餐廳或酒吧尋找「獵物」，使對方放下戒心後，即下藥並將受害人帶返住所侵犯。其中一名三十二歲受害女子供稱，在一六年四月於餐廳認識該對情侶，被邀參加船上派對。不料她被下藥，並帶到羅比切奧斯的住所迷姦。另一名受害女子在同年十月，在酒吧遭兩人灌醉，清醒時發現自己正遭侵犯；她遂尖叫求救，鄰居聞聲報警。<br />\n<br />\n橙縣檢察官拉考拉斯直指兩人是「披着羊皮的狼」。上述案件揭發後，探員在調查中順藤摸瓜，於羅比切奧斯的手機發現更多罪證，其後搜查羅比切奧斯住所，檢獲迷幻藥及可卡因，以及槍械等。<br />\n當局周二召開記者會，呼籲其他受害者挺身而出。<br />\n該對情侶各被控以強姦、性侵以及使用藥物和武器等多項罪名；羅比切奧斯另被控非法管有步槍、槍械、彈藥庫。一旦罪成，羅比切奧斯及賴利分別最高可被判囚四十年及三十年零八個月。兩人的律師否認指控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180920/mobile/odn-20180920-0920_00180_023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180920%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180920-0920_00180_023.html&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ced5db14\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180920/mobile/odn-20180920-0920_00180_023.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180920/photo/0920-00180-023b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180920%2Fphoto%2F0920-00180-023b1.jpg&h=f14ffca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180920/photo/0920-00180-023b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180920%2Fphoto%2F0920-00180-023b2.jpg&h=7fc0fb47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有條女幫手，Ｄ正妹戒心一定少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951d82274632fb8d3f3c1f57bf9dd426769ac032","tid":828942,"uid":56467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"好強既性慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cf4685cc6313d028abbba31b1aabc30b7c97e0","tid":828942,"uid":17213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"呢條鬼佬五官好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f484d5cbd269f5729f62a92b96a6a916aa0e1e0","tid":828942,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"77cf4685cc6313d028abbba31b1aabc30b7c97e0","tid":828942,"uid":17213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"呢條鬼佬五官好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/132801_13c07be2eb418507d43aa03f825a5108.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F132801_13c07be2eb418507d43aa03f825a5108.png&h=48f057e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20179b537421371b949e39ab6b67c4f9954f495a","tid":828942,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"條女正到，咁都要犯法"},{"pid":"ad1dbbf3c5d6b9b3ae017a2212af875b795f0ef5","tid":828942,"uid":196321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"我地香港都有小姓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c449b9f87d76f8468b9a7ce51c84ed25bbc5598b","tid":828942,"uid":83060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"華裔女性莫講話見到靚仔屌緊，就算係李宗瑞咁嘅款都扢起個頭去打茄輪。<br />\n<br />\n例子 : 余太"},{"pid":"863a74e6adf0ed0dbc65427b800d33ec9df4eaef","tid":828942,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score